'''Skip 1''' was the primary [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroid]] that was part of [[Smuggler's Run/Legends|Smuggler's Run]]. It was home to a [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]] and massive [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggling]] facility, as well as the typical locales associated with smugglers, including [[Cantina/Legends|cantinas]] and [[Casino/Legends|casinos]]. Navigating the asteroid field was very treacherous, thus making Smuggler's Run a very secure hideout. Skip 1 was the largest of several asteroids named "Skip". The asteroid almost exploded once due to a mysterious slime.

==History==
[[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] and some of his [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] associates had quarters there, and by [[17 ABY/Legends|17 ABY]], these had been abandoned and converted into an eating area. Later that year, Skip 1 was damaged after [[Droid/Legends|droids]] containing bombs, which were meant to be smuggled to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] as part of [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] [[Kueller]]'s [[Almanian Uprising|New Rebellion]], exploded, resulting in the [[Death/Legends|deaths]] of a number of [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]]. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] managed to save some of the injured, by flying them to the nearby [[Wrea/Legends|Wrea]] system for treatment.

